channel.title: 508 running problems
channel.description: Hey guys, ive just changed to a 508 server, but im having problems making it even run. When I click run server I get the error of "The system cannot find the path specified". When i click run on the client , it gets up to "Connecting to update server" and i get the error of "error_game_js5connect". This might be really ovious to some people but it isnt for me. Thanks for the help guys =)
